snippet.title: AMBER HEARD PARODY- DOGGIE SMUGGLING APOLOGY- AUSTRALIA
snippet.description:
Hi guys! my name is Carla Yang, Welcome to my channel! 
Hope you having an amazing day today!

Today's video is an Amber Heard Parody created for entertainment purposes regarding the incident with the dogs and Australia back in 2015.

Disclaimer: this video was created for entertainment purposes only, although sources shared down below are reliable, all information is alleged on my behalf; All information researched through the sources has been used to create entertaining content. Please do your own research if interested in knowing more into this case.
